Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • local.Node
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NodeNotificator
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Master

    public class Node
extends java.lang.Object
implements NodeNotificator
    Class represents slave node, that runs on remote pc managed by Master. Main function is sending MsgHello and responding to messages. Response may be sending a message or create the transaction and cede management to it.
    Author:
    Ivan Straka
